Templates.template:
new sap.chart.Chart(
	"${sId}", // string
	{
		id: ${id}, // sap.ui.core.ID
		models: ${models}, // object
		bindingContexts: ${bindingContexts}, // object
		objectBindings: ${objectBindings}, // object
		validationSuccess: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		validationError: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		parseError: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		formatError: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		modelContextChange: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		tooltip: ${tooltip}, // sap.ui.core.TooltipBase
		customData: [${customData}], // sap.ui.core.CustomData[]
		layoutData: ${layoutData}, // sap.ui.core.LayoutData
		dependents: [${dependents}], // sap.ui.core.Element[]
		busy: ${bBusy}, // boolean
		busyIndicatorDelay: ${1000}, // int
		visible: ${bVisible}, // boolean
		fieldGroupIds: ${[]}, // string[]
		validateFieldGroup: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		uiConfig: ${uiConfig}, // object
		width: ${"640px"}, // sap.ui.core.CSSSize
		height: ${"480px"}, // sap.ui.core.CSSSize
		chartType: ${"bar"}, // string
		uiConfig: ${uiConfig}, // object
		visibleDimensions: ${[]}, // string[]
		inResultDimensions: ${[]}, // string[]
		visibleMeasures: ${[]}, // string[]
		vizProperties: ${vizProperties}, // object
		vizScales: [${vizScales}], // object[]
		isAnalytical: ${bIsAnalytical}, // boolean
		selectionBehavior: ${"DATAPOINT"}, // string
		selectionMode: ${"sap.chart.SelectionMode.Multi"}, // string
		enablePagination: ${bEnablePagination}, // boolean
		data: [${data}], // sap.ui.core.Element[]
		dimensions: [${dimensions}], // sap.chart.data.Dimension[]
		measures: [${measures}], // sap.chart.data.Measure[]
		drilledDown: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		drilledUp: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		renderComplete: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		selectData: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		deselectData: [function (oEvent) {}, this] // function|array
	}
)
Templates.constructorDescription:
Constructor for a new Chart. Accepts an object literal mSettings that defines initial property values, aggregated and associated objects as well as event handlers. See {@link sap.ui.base.ManagedObject#constructor} for a general description of the syntax of the settings object. The supported settings are:
  • Properties
    • {@link #getChartType chartType} : string (default: bar)
    • {@link #getUiConfig uiConfig} : object
    • {@link #getVisibleDimensions visibleDimensions} : string[] (default: [])
    • {@link #getInResultDimensions inResultDimensions} : string[] (default: [])
    • {@link #getVisibleMeasures visibleMeasures} : string[] (default: [])
    • {@link #getVizProperties vizProperties} : object
    • {@link #getVizScales vizScales} : object[]
    • {@link #getIsAnalytical isAnalytical} : boolean
    • {@link #getSelectionBehavior selectionBehavior} : string (default: DATAPOINT)
    • {@link #getSelectionMode selectionMode} : string (default: sap.chart.SelectionMode.Multi)
    • {@link #getEnablePagination enablePagination} : boolean (default: false)
  • Aggregations
    • {@link #getData data} : sap.ui.core.Element[]
    • {@link #getDimensions dimensions} : sap.chart.data.Dimension[]
    • {@link #getMeasures measures} : sap.chart.data.Measure[]
  • Events
    • {@link #event:drilledDown drilledDown} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:drilledUp drilledUp} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:renderComplete renderComplete} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:selectData selectData} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:deselectData deselectData} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
In addition, all settings applicable to the base type {@link sap.viz.ui5.controls.common.BaseControl#constructor sap.viz.ui5.controls.common.BaseControl} can be used as well.
Templates.name: sap.chart.Chart
